## Layout Integration
AppBar should be the first element in your page component:
```html
<div class="page-wrapper">
  <!-- AppBar first -->
  <ejs-appbar cssClass="custom-appbar">
    <!-- ... -->
  </ejs-appbar>

  <!-- Then page content -->
  <div class="page-content">
    <!-- ... -->
  </div>
</div>
```

## Page Content Spacing
Remove top padding from page wrapper when using AppBar:
```scss
.page-wrapper {
  // No top padding - AppBar handles it
}

.page-content {
  padding: 0 20px 20px 20px; // Only sides and bottom
}
```

## Responsive Behavior
AppBar automatically handles responsive behavior:
- Full width on all screen sizes
- Buttons stack on mobile if needed
- Text truncates gracefully

