## Do's and Don'ts
✅ **DO**:
- Use `cssClass="custom-appbar"` for consistent styling
- Use emoji icons for visual consistency
- Include descriptive subtitles
- Use `e-appbar-spacer` for button alignment
- Use teal gradient background

❌ **DON'T**:
- Create custom headers instead of using AppBar
- Hardcode colors (use SCSS variables/gradients)
- Add padding around AppBar (it's full-width)
- Use text-only titles without emoji icons
